column2: ENGLISH
Create duchy
Create a titular duchy from the [Root.GetFullBaseName].
Create kingdom
Create a titular kingdom from the [Root.GetFullBaseName].
Create empire
Create a titular empire from the [Root.GetFullBaseName].
Designate receiving duchy
Designate the [Root.GetFullBaseName] as the receiver for any future de jure county transfers. Any previously designated duchy will lose this designation.
Designate receiving kingdom
Designate the [Root.GetFullBaseName] as the receiver for any future de jure duchy transfers. Any previously designated kingdom will lose this designation.
Designate receiving empire
Designate the [Root.GetFullBaseName] as the receiver for any future de jure kingdom transfers. Any previously designated empire will lose this designation.
Transfer county
The [Root.GetFullBaseName] becomes a de jure part of the currently designated duchy.
Transfer duchy
The [Root.GetFullBaseName] becomes a de jure part of the currently designated kingdom.
Transfer kingdom
The [Root.GetFullBaseName] becomes a de jure part of the currently designated empire.
